---
title: Honey-Mustard Ham Steak with Cranberry Green Beans and Creamy Chive Smashed Potato
description: Ham steaks with a sweet and zesty glaze, creamy chive smashed potatoes and festive cranberry green beans will remind you of a holiday feast any night of the week!
